	h2 And then it snowed 
	.story Later that afternon, it snowed heavily for the first time since we can came to Nellim. Feeling like kids encountering snow for the first time, we played in it. The snow tickles when it lands on your face and melts. The dry air in Nellim creates powdery snow. If you fling a snow ball, it burst into a mist of snow upon impact. Now, stand back and laugh at the person jumping up and down because the snow has gone inside the clothes.
